snippet: There’s a divide between older moderates and a growing group of progressive and diverse voters.
lead_paragraph: When Joe Biden first ran for Senate in 1972, 40 percent of Democrats believed that whites had a right to segregate neighborhoods.

snippet: President Trump promised to be the champion of the “forgotten American.” To some Republicans in Altoona, that promise is unfulfilled.
lead_paragraph: ALTOONA, Pa. — President Trump’s road to re-election runs through places like Altoona, with its deep working-class roots, conservative social values and nearly all-white population. But it is not a straight line.
abstract: President Trump promised to be the champion of the “forgotten American.” To some Republicans in Altoona, that promise is unfulfilled.

snippet: Noah said that while Elizabeth Warren and Kamala Harris came to the CNN town hall armed with actual policies, Pete Buttigieg apparently tried to wing it.

abstract: The Supreme Court’s conservative majority seems poised to allow the Trump administration to add a question on citizenship to the 2020 census.

snippet: Mr. Biden, ahead in the polls but behind financially, is seeking out top money bundlers, but that risks a backlash among grass-roots Democrats.
lead_paragraph: Former Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr. is going to have to raise money like he’s never raised money before.
abstract: Mr. Biden, ahead in the polls but behind financially, is seeking out top money bundlers, but that risks a backlash among grass-roots Democrats.

snippet: Now what should the Democrats do about it?
lead_paragraph: Bret Stephens: Hi Gail. I know neither of us can wait to debate the best name for Meghan Markle’s and Prince Harry’s royal baby, but can we first discuss the small matter of the Mueller report? How do you see it playing out, politically speaking, for President Trump?
abstract: Now what should the Democrats do about it?

snippet: The Vermont senator has been the front-runner in early campaigning, but Mr. Biden’s expected entry could change that. Mr. Sanders is not likely to care.
lead_paragraph: PITTSBURGH — Senator Bernie Sanders was in a rush.
